      "comment": "JONATHAN'S DREAM (1) last raced on January 8 when fifth (26.80) over 460m at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Has a good record here at this journey. Drawn the fence and expected to go close. MISS BLACK (5) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh at this track, but was among the placings at Sandown three back. Has the ability and can find best this time. ROMAN EMPIRE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 400m behind Vinnie's Camel (24.05) in a Grade 5. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. JOHN BOY (8) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
